name: Inferno Maw Refrigerator
text: The Inferno Maw Refrigerator stood looming in the Enchanted Kitchen, its fiery gaze attracting bewitched apples. The villagers whispered of its endless hunger, fearful it would one day devour their feast. Yet the bravest soul dared to befriend the beast, learning it yearned not for food, but companionship.
